short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Download your Sololearn codes as a zip file.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Export/Download your codes on Sololearn with ease, just download this extension (no extra setup required), and visit someone's Sololearn profile, in their code bits section a new button named "Export Codes" will appear (reload once if the button doesn't appear), export the codes using that button, it will be downloaded as a zip file,
where each code is a folder containing a metadata.json and the source code files.
Sololearn Backup can export the private codes too if you are logged in, it can also be used to export other person's public codes.

Author: Arnav (https://github.com/arnav-kr)
GitHub Repo: https://github.com/arnav-kr/SLBackup
